  <brief_title>Immunogenicity of a Surface Antigen, Inactivated Influenza Vaccine Formulation 2007-2008</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II, Open-Label, Uncontrolled, Single Center Study to Evaluate Safety and Immunogenicity of a Surface Antigen, Inactivated Influenza Vaccine Ph.Eur, Formulation 2007-2008, When Administered to Non-Elderly Adult and Elderly Subjects</official_title>
